## Extended features

| Tool | When to use |
|------|-------------|
| `memory_pre_compact` | Pre-compact hook: store raw messages + session summary before context is compacted |
| `memory_chat_history_store` | Per-turn: save raw messages (use memory_pre_compact for full session checkpoint) |
| `memory_chat_history_list` | List saved chat history (newest first) |
| `memory_suggest_recall` | Before responding: get related topics to recall |
| `memory_analytics` | Check recall hit rate, cache hits, token usage (local) |
| `memory_resource_working_set` | Get pack as resource for subscription pattern |
| `memory_recall_compact(..., as_of_ts)` | Point-in-time: what did we know at time T? |
| `memory_recall_new_since(namespace, since_ts)` | Session start: what's new since last_session_end (~50–100 tokens) |
| `memory_recall_headlines(namespace, query)` | Headlines-only (~150 tokens); then memory_expand for needed IDs |
| `memory_recall_compact(..., entity_bundle=true)` | Group facts/decisions by entity |
| `memory_recall_compact(..., timeline_collapse=true)` | Timeline by date; use `timeline_by_date[].pointer_ids` with memory_expand |
| `memory_recall_compact(..., granularity=macro)` | Hierarchical: macro (~50 tokens), medium (256), micro (full) |
| `memory_expand(..., granularity=medium|full)` | Override mode: medium=summary_256, full=content |
| `memory_ingest(..., items[].version)` | Skill versioning for procedural memories |
| Ingest returns `potential_contradictions` | Review when adding conflicting info |

