## Team tools

Use when coordinating work, decisions, or handoffs. All require `namespace`.

| Tool | When to use |
|------|-------------|
| `team_decision_propose` | Propose a decision; link `evidence_node_ids` from recall pointers |
| `team_decision_list` | List decisions (proposed, accepted, etc.) |
| `team_decision_accept` | Accept a decision |
| `team_decision_vote` | Vote on a decision |
| `team_task_create` | Create task; set assignee, priority, `blocked_by`, `memory_node_ids` |
| `team_task_list` | List tasks (optionally by assignee) |
| `team_task_update` | Update task status/assignee |
| `team_handoff_create` | Handoff to another role: `from_role`, `to_role`, `changes`, `how_to_test`, `risks` |
| `team_handoff_read` | Read latest handoff for a role |
| `team_contract_set` | Set API spec, DB schema, deploy process (versioned; key e.g. "api-spec", "db-schema") |
| `team_contract_get` | Get current contract version |
| `team_contract_diff` | Diff contract versions |
| `team_lock_acquire` / `team_lock_release` | Lock shared resources |
| `team_conflict_open` / `team_conflict_resolve` | Open and resolve conflicts |
| `team_digest` | Standup/awareness: activity since timestamp |
| `team_who_knows` | Find who knows about an entity |
| `team_role_assign` | Assign roles |
| `team_ceo_annotate` | Claim–Evidence–Owner for traceability |
